name: Mirror Mirror on the Wall #1
description:
Inspired by the song Supermodel by Sza.
"I could be your supermodel
If you believe
If you see it in me
I don't see myself
Why I can't stay alone just by myself?
Wish I was comfortable just with myself
But I need you"
The struggle to see the goods in yourself, to be comfortable and accept yourself. The imperfect woman trying to see herself on the mirror trying to be her own supermodel.
